OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FItaly: Statue of           
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fscantily-clad woman sparks 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fsexism row                 
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A bronze statue of a scantily-clad     
OL,6, woman to honour a 19th Century poem has
OL,7, sparked a sexism row in Italy, with    
OL,8, politicians calling for its removal.   
OL,10,FThe sculpture in the southern town of  
OL,11,FSapri is a tribute to La Spigolatrice  
OL,12,Fdi Sapri (The Gleaner of Sapri),       
OL,13,Fwritten by Luigi Mercantini in 1857.   
OL,15,FIt portrays a woman in a transparent   
OL,16,Fdress with one arm over her breasts.   
OL,18,FCongresswoman Laura Boldrini said the  
OL,19,Fstatue was "an offense to women and to 
OL,20,Fthe history it should celebrate".      
